1112
01:13:27,442 --> 01:13:29,098
Don't get mad

1113
01:13:30,169 --> 01:13:32,424
Well, she's has no men right now

1114
01:13:34,580 --> 01:13:39,611
But what I'm saying is, you never know when she'll find a man

1115
01:13:40,410 --> 01:13:42,334
You never know what's going to happen in the future

1116
01:13:43,499 --> 01:13:46,254
So you don't like if she takes over?

1117
01:13:50,322 --> 01:13:53,822
I've been making it since your father's time

1118
01:13:54,230 --> 01:13:56,319
so I'm not thinking about my own selfish gain

1119
01:13:57,400 --> 01:14:00,400
A woman can understand a woman when she sees her

1120
01:14:00,720 --> 01:14:03,339
You just met her today

1121
01:14:05,832 --> 01:14:06,898
Young master

1122
01:14:08,058 --> 01:14:12,957
When I spoke to you the other day, I asked the Private Investigation Agency to look into it

1123
01:14:16,460 --> 01:14:19,907
Of course, I don't take these things at face value

1124
01:14:20,440 --> 01:14:25,306
She's met a lot of different people, like
novelists and painters

1125
01:14:26,470 --> 01:14:27,410
She's a bar girl

1126
01:14:27,435 --> 01:14:29,311
Well, there must have been a lot in the past

1127
01:14:29,820 --> 01:14:31,262
But I'm aware of that too

1128
01:14:33,693 --> 01:14:34,847
I got it

1129
01:14:35,380 --> 01:14:37,436
