1130
01:14:37,460 --> 01:14:39,530
Let's take a closer look

1131
01:14:42,430 --> 01:14:45,430
I guess you haven't talked about taking her here yet

1132
01:14:47,317 --> 01:14:47,684
Not yet.

1133
01:14:48,873 --> 01:14:51,873
And the antiques teacher who is also there

1134
01:14:53,110 --> 01:14:56,110
I'm a bit curious about that person too

1135
01:14:59,494 --> 01:15:01,309
I get so drunk today

1136
01:15:02,078 --> 01:15:03,111
It's rare.

1137
01:15:03,990 --> 01:15:05,796
You aren't drunk at all yet

1138
01:15:07,770 --> 01:15:10,770
It would be a problem if Oyone disliked me for drinking

1139
01:15:12,272 --> 01:15:12,912
Oyo

1140
01:15:14,349 --> 01:15:18,384
You're a girl who can't stand the lifestyle,

1141
01:15:19,440 --> 01:15:21,229
but this time you'll have to be patient

1142
01:15:22,550 --> 01:15:24,633
If you feel like you're dead, there's nothing I can't do

1143
01:15:26,313 --> 01:15:30,187
I'm going to work hard and not make you suffer financially this time

1144
01:15:30,480 --> 01:15:32,569
Don't care about me

1145
01:15:34,850 --> 01:15:37,850
Hey, Oyone is kind of nice

1146
01:15:39,920 --> 01:15:41,927
I want to be like her when I get older

1147
01:15:43,800 --> 01:15:45,647
I think I'd get along well with that person.

1148
01:15:48,739 --> 01:15:49,765
I'm drunk

1149
01:15:55,979 --> 01:15:57,199
Are you alright?

1150
01:16:03,672 --> 01:16:05,925
I apologize for having to step away.

1151
01:16:06,023 --> 01:16:07,083
Oh you are here!

1152
01:16:09,087 --> 01:16:10,603
Tell Oyone

1153
01:16:10,983 --> 01:16:12,577
Oyo has no men besides me

1154
01:16:13,390 --> 01:16:14,505
I am her man

1155
01:16:16,839 --> 01:16:18,549
Hey, where is my room?

1156
01:16:18,580 --> 01:16:19,586
I'll show you

1157
01:16:19,611 --> 01:16:20,369
Teacher

1158
01:16:21,585 --> 01:16:22,420
Good night

1159
01:16:28,911 --> 01:16:33,259
Is it really that unusual for someone like
Takashima to drink alcohol in a hot spring?

1160
01:16:35,030 --> 01:16:37,345
The teacher was very happy with this story

1161
01:16:40,140 --> 01:16:42,286
What did Oyone say?

1162
01:16:43,592 --> 01:16:46,592
she said you should try helping her out until you get used to it

1163
01:16:48,559 --> 01:16:50,017
Will I be able to work?

1164
01:16:50,760 --> 01:16:53,197
That's why she thinks of me
as his real son

1165
01:16:54,413 --> 01:16:55,945
She cares about you a lot too.

1166
01:16:58,040 --> 01:17:01,259
What a wonderful garden

1167
01:17:02,868 --> 01:17:06,212
How nice it would be to live
a relaxed life in such a fresh air

1168
01:17:09,940 --> 01:17:14,415
I'm tired of going back to cramped bars and apartments

1169
01:17:15,844 --> 01:17:17,353
When I think about it like this,

1170
01:17:18,320 --> 01:17:19,994
it seems like I've been dead until now

1171
01:17:22,390 --> 01:17:23,908
I won't let you feel that way.

1172
01:18:18,853 --> 01:18:20,010
Come on, let's go.

1173
01:18:38,635 --> 01:18:39,350
I'm back.

1174
01:18:39,375 --> 01:18:40,267
Welcome back.

1175
01:18:46,244 --> 01:18:48,674
Mr. President of Kofu is here.

1176
01:18:55,916 --> 01:18:56,892
I'm back.

1177
01:18:57,080 --> 01:18:58,330
Welcome back.

1178
01:19:00,035 --> 01:19:01,072
Thank you for your hard work

1179
01:19:04,680 --> 01:19:07,136
How is it? Have you gotten used to it?

1180
01:19:07,885 --> 01:19:08,666
I think so.

1181
01:19:09,971 --> 01:19:10,923
That's a good thing

1182
01:19:13,752 --> 01:19:14,768
By the way.

1183
01:19:15,354 --> 01:19:18,354
I was just talking to Oyone-san,

1184
01:19:20,426 --> 01:19:23,426
but can you please break up with Takashima-san?

1185
01:19:26,500 --> 01:19:28,896
What do you mean by break up?

1186
01:19:28,920 --> 01:19:31,275
if the way I say things like this is wrong,

1187
01:19:32,020 --> 01:19:35,020
I'd rather you just not have him to come here anymore

1188
01:19:37,151 --> 01:19:39,353
Apparently he stayed for two nights while I was away

1189
01:19:39,455 --> 01:19:39,838
Non-chan

1190
01:19:39,870 --> 01:19:48,172
Also, I didn't want to say this, but I'm causing financial trouble to Takashima-san

1191
01:19:48,870 --> 01:19:51,103
Well, it's not a huge amount

1192
01:19:52,192 --> 01:19:54,098
Even so, If it is made public

1193
01:19:54,152 --> 01:19:55,444
He is a fraudster

1194
01:19:59,090 --> 01:20:00,994
If you want to bring it up,

1195
01:20:01,490 --> 01:20:03,266
Can I settle the matter?

1196
01:20:07,594 --> 01:20:08,751
What do you think?

1197
01:20:08,776 --> 01:20:10,056
You just keep quiet.

1198
01:20:17,360 --> 01:20:20,016
Hello? yes

1199
01:20:21,001 --> 01:20:22,392
He's here.

1200
01:20:23,100 --> 01:20:25,337
From the Tokyo branch

1201
01:20:26,025 --> 01:20:27,705
I will pass it on to you.

1202
01:20:29,244 --> 01:20:30,603
Please

1203
01:20:30,916 --> 01:20:31,572
Yes?

1204
01:20:34,814 --> 01:20:35,932
I know

1205
01:20:37,240 --> 01:20:38,267
What?

1206
01:20:40,590 --> 01:20:42,134
Of course I've paid

1207
01:20:43,450 --> 01:20:45,337
We were just talking about that now

1208
01:20:46,690 --> 01:20:49,690
I guess I should have told you first so as not to make things too complicated

1209
01:20:52,375 --> 01:20:54,697
I'm going there tomorrow morning at 10 o'clock.

1210
01:21:06,232 --> 01:21:06,992
Yo-chan.

1211
01:21:08,840 --> 01:21:10,181
Well, you remember this, right?

1212
01:21:12,284 --> 01:21:13,919
Apparently Takashima did it again

1213
01:21:14,900 --> 01:21:20,522
Apparently, the only things that haven't been given to the other party are the 200,000 yen that I paid for this and the Kiseto cup I bought later

1214
01:21:20,990 --> 01:21:23,636
My company has just received an inquiry

1215
01:21:23,660 --> 01:21:26,660
It turned out I hadn't paid

1216
01:21:26,990 --> 01:21:32,248
It's sad that people only think about what happens if they worry about it

1217
01:21:33,805 --> 01:21:36,227
Isn't this the right time?

1218
01:21:36,676 --> 01:21:37,496
Yoko.

1219
01:21:47,720 --> 01:21:49,368
Thank you.

1220
01:21:53,015 --> 01:21:54,218
Oh I see.

1221
01:21:56,586 --> 01:22:00,274
Yo-chan has gone to Yugawara for a week

1222
01:22:03,259 --> 01:22:05,365
Mom is  in the hospital

1223
01:22:05,390 --> 01:22:06,691
No customers will come if we keep doing this.

1224
01:22:11,752 --> 01:22:13,285
Welcome.

1225
01:22:15,340 --> 01:22:16,200
Welcome.

1226
01:22:16,251 --> 01:22:17,921
It's been a while, teacher

1227
01:22:18,108 --> 01:22:18,768
It's been a while

1228
01:22:20,087 --> 01:22:21,149
What would you like?

1229
01:22:22,095 --> 01:22:23,366
You like whiskey,right?

1230
01:22:23,390 --> 01:22:23,988
Yes

1231
01:22:24,975 --> 01:22:26,022
How about Takashima?

1232
01:22:27,740 --> 01:22:29,954
He hasn’t seen me in a while

1233
01:22:39,360 --> 01:22:40,646
That's a good place to be

1234
01:22:41,221 --> 01:22:42,234
In the end

1235
01:22:50,152 --> 01:22:52,147
Is Madame suffering from breast sick?

1236
01:22:52,220 --> 01:22:54,606
She collapsed after New Year's

1237
01:22:54,630 --> 01:22:55,885
That's a big problem

1238
01:23:02,530 --> 01:23:03,466
Sometimes when I come here

1239
01:23:03,490 --> 01:23:04,698
I feel a bit strange.

1240
01:23:10,566 --> 01:23:11,392
Welcome

1241
01:23:13,400 --> 01:23:14,729
Haven't you lost some weight?

1242
01:23:15,109 --> 01:23:15,969
You think so?

1243
01:23:16,876 --> 01:23:17,892
You look better

1244
01:23:20,340 --> 01:23:22,407
You've calmed down too

1245
01:23:22,690 --> 01:23:24,764
Yeah, it seems

1246
01:23:26,163 --> 01:23:28,027
You were always frustrated back then

1247
01:23:28,525 --> 01:23:30,265
but there were good things too

1248
01:23:30,900 --> 01:23:32,899
We met around here at Yugawara Station

1249
01:23:34,680 --> 01:23:36,791
I really wanted to call out to you

1250
01:23:37,573 --> 01:23:38,453
Same here.

1251
01:23:40,019 --> 01:23:41,365
Let's go to Box

1252
01:23:41,841 --> 01:23:43,347
Welcome

1253
01:23:45,064 --> 01:23:46,057
Welcome

1254
01:23:46,872 --> 01:23:47,799
Welcome

1255
01:23:49,039 --> 01:23:52,937
I heard you met a good husband and going to stay at Yugarwara Inn

1256
01:23:54,009 --> 01:23:56,129
Takashima-sensei tells me to be patient,

1257
01:23:56,399 --> 01:23:58,516
It's his habit to tell you to be patient

1258
01:24:00,903 --> 01:24:02,617
When it was my turn, he told me to break up

1259
01:24:04,978 --> 01:24:06,112
Did you feel resentful?

1260
01:24:06,760 --> 01:24:09,760
Or did you not listen to what he said?

1261
01:24:11,299 --> 01:24:14,299
You've always disliked Takashima-sensei

1262
01:24:14,820 --> 01:24:15,856
For me,

1263
01:24:15,880 --> 01:24:18,880
I hate the way women treat each other

1264
01:24:19,830 --> 01:24:22,830
He's actually in love with you but he's scared to sleep with you

1265
01:24:24,650 --> 01:24:27,650
That's why he despises people who are with you

1266
01:24:29,270 --> 01:24:33,868
He's trying to win your heart by selling the fact that he won't hold your hand

1267
01:24:35,840 --> 01:24:37,608
I don't want to hand you over to that guy

1268
01:24:40,930 --> 01:24:43,930
But I'll follow him.

1269
01:24:46,556 --> 01:24:51,966
You've been in dealing with various
men for a long time in the Ginza bar world

1270
01:24:53,970 --> 01:24:55,896
When you're in this business,

1271
01:24:55,920 --> 01:24:58,920
you start to get tired of being connected only to guys

1272
01:25:00,306 --> 01:25:01,757
At times like that

1273
01:25:02,173 --> 01:25:06,880
A man like Takashima looks so beautiful and impressive for you

1274
01:25:10,863 --> 01:25:12,656
I think that's the kind of relationship you have

1275
01:25:13,926 --> 01:25:17,399
It's dangerous to follow a man like him

1276
01:25:17,860 --> 01:25:20,860
It's like blind person is pulling blind person's hand

1277
01:25:22,580 --> 01:25:24,010
Aren't you blind person?

1278
01:25:27,100 --> 01:25:30,100
I don't care about such troublesome things anymore

1279
01:25:33,553 --> 01:25:38,482
When I think about it now, it all seems like a long time ago

1280
01:25:41,840 --> 01:25:45,855
One day I tagged along on your trip to the park to see the cherry blossoms in Yoshino

1281
01:25:46,260 --> 01:25:47,936
Oh it was beautiful

1282
01:25:49,800 --> 01:25:52,373
I didn't even notice the flowers blooming this year

1283
01:25:52,940 --> 01:25:54,048
Has it already scattered?

1284
01:25:56,020 --> 01:25:58,826
That's right, the evening paper was out

1285
01:25:58,850 --> 01:26:06,069
I'd like to see the cherry blossoms in front of the British Embassy, Benkei Bridge, Aoyama Cemetery, or somewhere else

1286
01:26:06,914 --> 01:26:08,074
I'd like to see

1287
01:26:10,370 --> 01:26:11,467
Shall we take there now?

1288
01:26:47,043 --> 01:26:48,204
It's so pretty

1289
01:26:51,022 --> 01:26:51,982
It's so pretty

1290
01:26:54,513 --> 01:26:56,328
I feel like eating it.

1291
01:27:00,890 --> 01:27:02,710
I'm not going home tonight

1292
01:27:04,096 --> 01:27:06,885
You're the one who went back to your wife and daughter

1293
01:27:07,380 --> 01:27:08,572
You're going to Yugawara,right?

1294
01:27:09,726 --> 01:27:11,012
For Takashima-san's sake

1295
01:27:16,510 --> 01:27:17,830
I won't be going home tonight

1296
01:27:34,703 --> 01:27:35,223
OK

1297
01:27:38,290 --> 01:27:41,290
In return, I'll play with you just for today

1298
01:27:44,161 --> 01:27:44,848
Yoko...

1299
01:27:47,550 --> 01:27:49,638
Because the cherry blossoms are blooming

1300
01:28:17,155 --> 01:28:19,571
I'm pretty sure Oyo was born around here too

1301
01:28:20,166 --> 01:28:25,952
My grandmother, who loved me, often took me
to the Juban night market when I was a child

1302
01:28:26,800 --> 01:28:28,211
How is Mishima's mother?

1303
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:32,536
I'm planning to send her a letter tonight

1304
01:28:32,560 --> 01:28:33,236
Tonight?

1305
01:28:48,914 --> 01:28:49,777
Teacher

1306
01:28:51,731 --> 01:28:52,544
I’m sorry.

1307
01:28:54,680 --> 01:28:57,122
I couldn't hold back in Yugawara
after all

1308
01:28:58,479 --> 01:29:03,543
I tried my best, but I'm really sorry,

1309
01:29:03,780 --> 01:29:05,331
You are such an idiot

1310
01:29:06,905 --> 01:29:08,892
You didn't care if
it was for me

1311
01:29:09,650 --> 01:29:11,626
Did the other party bring it up?

1312
01:29:11,674 --> 01:29:12,388
No, didn't

1313
01:29:13,692 --> 01:29:16,881
He tell you to break up with me?

1314
01:29:19,028 --> 01:29:22,531
I was the one who said I wanted to break up with you

1315
01:29:24,910 --> 01:29:28,678
In return...I never want to see that person's face again

1316
01:29:28,875 --> 01:29:33,068
I didn't mean to ruin your conversation,

1317
01:29:33,500 --> 01:29:36,500
but I've been pressed for money for the mansion's lawsuit

1318
01:29:36,690 --> 01:29:38,136
It's not the teacher's fault

1319
01:29:38,160 --> 01:29:40,201
Of course, I had planned to cover the expenses.

1320
01:29:48,373 --> 01:29:51,373
Well, this is also going to happen

1321
01:29:52,530 --> 01:29:56,389
Speaking of things happening,
things are strange between you and me

1322
01:29:57,602 --> 01:29:59,808
I'd only ever been jealous of once

1323
01:30:01,145 --> 01:30:03,099
It was when I was in Yugawara for the first time

1324
01:30:05,196 --> 01:30:08,196
You were really drunk that time

1325
01:30:09,312 --> 01:30:11,609
but maybe it was because the other person was a rich guy

1326
01:30:25,063 --> 01:30:25,870
Teacher?

1327
01:30:27,860 --> 01:30:28,964
I'm going to die

1328
01:30:31,896 --> 01:30:33,225
That's already decided

1329
01:30:34,114 --> 01:30:35,538
Don't be stupid

1330
01:30:35,778 --> 01:30:36,765
You are beautiful

1331
01:30:37,450 --> 01:30:38,608
The flowers still bloom

1332
01:30:41,080 --> 01:30:42,903
I want to die while I'm still beautiful

1333
01:30:45,690 --> 01:30:47,568
No human being is worth committing suicide for

1334
01:31:38,297 --> 01:31:39,691
Thank you very much.

1335
01:31:48,212 --> 01:31:49,505
You left your underwear

1336
01:32:12,557 --> 01:32:17,642
The letter was a suicide note addressed to his mother-in-law in Mishima

1337
01:32:25,675 --> 01:32:28,262
I'll send you the apartment keys

1338
01:32:34,030 --> 01:32:36,606
Although we are not related by blood,

1339
01:32:36,630 --> 01:32:40,612
thank you for raising me since I was little

1340
01:32:43,860 --> 01:32:45,808
This is the last time,

1341
01:32:46,420 --> 01:32:49,420
so please clean up after yourself

1342
01:32:50,290 --> 01:32:52,216
I'm like a found child,

1343
01:32:53,066 --> 01:32:54,400
so don't put me in the grave

1344
01:32:54,540 --> 01:32:56,973
I would be happier if they turned it into an abandoned grave

1345
01:32:57,132 --> 01:33:01,473
and put it in a temple somewhere in Tokyo

1346
01:33:04,875 --> 01:33:08,409
The apartment deposit should be enough money

1347
01:33:10,961 --> 01:33:18,492
I think you're just saying selfish things and not expressing your true feelings

1348
01:33:19,763 --> 01:33:24,097
Maybe that's what leaving a note is all about

1349
01:33:28,550 --> 01:33:32,705
I don't want anyone to know that I'm dead

1350
01:33:35,150 --> 01:33:36,941
I am dying with such a good feeling,

1351
01:33:38,638 --> 01:33:42,453
so please don't cry or feel sorry for me.

1352
01:33:47,500 --> 01:33:48,700
Goodbye

1353
01:35:45,952 --> 01:35:48,679
She thought she was cleaning up quickly,

1354
01:35:49,369 --> 01:35:54,766
but Yoko might have actually been moving
around slowly

1355
01:36:07,343 --> 01:36:13,085
Suddenly she became worried that something had gone wrong

1356
01:36:13,110 --> 01:36:15,036
and she would fail

1357
01:36:15,493 --> 01:36:19,127
She was extremely angry
that such anxiety had arisen

1358
01:36:23,482 --> 01:36:26,637
Once she started to get angry, there was no stopping it

1359
01:36:27,380 --> 01:36:30,380
She got angry about everything and everything

1360
01:36:32,708 --> 01:36:38,254
To Matsuzaki, Junko, and Ayako...

1361
01:36:47,989 --> 01:36:52,122
She found the room very small and stuffy.

1362
01:36:55,670 --> 01:37:03,677
She was very angry at herself for living in such a small room.

1363
01:37:07,326 --> 01:37:11,685
She was upset about something she had spent so much time preparing.

1364
01:37:42,850 --> 01:37:45,850
However, when she finished taking the medicine,

1365
01:37:47,230 --> 01:37:50,230
something welled up in her chest,

1366
01:37:50,940 --> 01:37:53,940
and she thought she could finally cry

1367
01:37:54,183 --> 01:37:57,183
It didn't turn to tears.

1368
01:38:18,360 --> 01:38:20,125
And darkness came.

1369
01:38:41,629 --> 01:38:52,078
THE END

